<!doctype html>
<html lang="vi">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>📝 Game 3: Phiếu Quan Sát Con Vật</title>
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style/home.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style/secret.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style/style.css" />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css"
    />
    <style>
      .game-container {
        max-width: 750px;
      }
      .observation-area {
        background: #f8fafc;
        border: 4px solid #cbd5e1;
        border-radius: 30px;
        padding: 25px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 0 #cbd5e1;
      }
      .animal-preview {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        padding-bottom: 20px;
        border-bottom: 3px dashed #e2e8f0;
      }
      .animal-preview img {
        width: 180px;
        height: 180px;
        object-fit: cover;
        border-radius: 25px;
        border: 6px solid #ffe66d;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .animal-preview .big-emoji {
        font-size: 5rem;
        display: block;
      }
      .animal-preview .animal-title {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 900;
        color: #b45f2b;
        margin-top: 8px;
      }
      .trait-row {
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }
      .trait-label {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: #57606f;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        display: block;
      }
      .trait-options {
        display: flex;
        gap: 10px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }
      .trait-btn {
        background: #ffe8d4;
        border-radius: 50px;
        padding: 10px 24px;
        font-weight: 800;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        cursor: pointer;
        border: 3px solid #ffcf97;
        transition: 0.08s linear;
        color: #714623;
        font-family: "Nunito", sans-serif;
      }
      .trait-btn:active {
        transform: scale(0.95);
      }
      .trait-btn.selected {
        background: #ffcf9a;
        border-color: #c9924b;
        color: #4a2a10;
      }
      .trait-btn.correct-show {
        background: #c8e6b5 !important;
        border-color: #6f9e3f !important;
        color: #2e3d1a;
      }
      .trait-btn.wrong-show {
        background: #fbc4c4 !important;
        border-color: #e16363 !important;
        color: #8b1a1a;
      }
      .trait-btn.disabled {
        pointer-events: none;
        opacity: 0.7;
      }
      .check-btn {
        display: block;
        margin: 20px auto 0;
        padding: 14px 40px;
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        font-weight: 900;
        font-family: "Nunito", sans-serif;
        color: #ffffff;
        background: #c9924b;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 50px;
        cursor: pointer;
        box-shadow: 0 6px 0 #a67a3a;
        transition: all 0.2s;
      }
      .check-btn:active {
        transform: translateY(4px);
        box-shadow: none;
      }
      .progress-bar {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .progress-bar .dot {
        width: 18px;
        height: 18px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: #e2e8f0;
        border: 3px solid #cbd5e1;
        transition: all 0.2s;
      }
      .progress-bar .dot.active {
        background: #ffe0b5;
        border-color: #c9924b;
        transform: scale(1.2);
      }
      .progress-bar .dot.completed {
        background: #4cd137;
        border-color: #3bad29;
      }
      .feedback-box {
        text-align: center;
        font-weight: 800;
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        margin: 15px 0;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 20px;
      }
      .correct-fb {
        color: #2e7d32;
        background: #e8f5e9;
      }
      .wrong-fb {
        color: #c62828;
        background: #ffebee;
      }
      .next-btn {
        display: block;
        margin: 10px auto 0;
        padding: 14px 40px;
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        font-weight: 900;
        font-family: "Nunito", sans-serif;
        color: #ffffff;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5b775 0%, #c9924b 100%);
        border: none;
        border-radius: 50px;
        cursor: pointer;
        box-shadow:
          0 6px 0 #cc4141,
          0 10px 20px rgba(255, 82, 82, 0.25);
        transition: all 0.2s;
      }
      .next-btn:active {
        transform: translateY(4px);
        box-shadow:
          0 2px 0 #cc4141,
          0 5px 10px rgba(255, 82, 82, 0.35);
      }
      .hidden {
        display: none !important;
      }
      @media (max-width: 576px) {
        .observation-area {
          padding: 18px 15px;
        }
        .animal-preview img {
          width: 130px;
          height: 130px;
        }
        .animal-preview .big-emoji {
          font-size: 3.5rem;
        }
        .trait-options {
          flex-direction: column;
        }
        .trait-btn {
          width: 100%;
          text-align: center;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body class="secret-game-page">
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <div class="game-container">
      <header class="game-internal-header">
        <div class="score-board">🌟 <span id="sticker-count">0</span></div>
        <h1 style="color: #f2b779">📝 Phiếu Quan Sát Con Vật</h1>
        <p class="sub-title">
          Bé hãy quan sát và chọn đặc điểm của con vật nhé!
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="progress-bar" id="progress-bar"></div>

      <div class="observation-area">
        <div class="animal-preview">
          <div id="animal-display"></div>
          <div class="animal-title" id="animal-title">Con Vật</div>
        </div>

        <div id="traits-container"></div>

        <div class="feedback-box hidden" id="feedback-box"></div>

        <button class="check-btn" id="check-btn">✅ Kiểm tra</button>
        <button class="next-btn hidden" id="next-btn">Câu tiếp theo ➡️</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="finish-modal" class="modal">
      <div class="modal-content">
        <h2>👑 BÉ THẬT LÀ SIÊU! 👑</h2>
        <p>Bé đã quan sát và mô tả được đặc điểm của các con vật rồi!</p>
        <div class="final-stickers">🌟 🌟 🌟</div>
        <button id="restart-btn">Chơi lại từ đầu nha</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/js/secret.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
